title: Vegan coffee cheesecake
ingredients: ['300g cashew nuts, soaked overnight', '8 pitted dates', '100g flaked almonds', '50g gluten free oats', '50g walnuts', '1 pinch salt', '4 tablespoons maple syrup', '100ml brewed coffee or espresso', '1 1/2 teaspoons vanilla extract', '5 tablespoons melted coconut oil']
